<v-card style="padding: 2%;">
  <v-form>
    <v-container>
      <v-row>
        <v-col cols="8">
          <v-text-field
            readonly
            dense
            :value="Event.Name"
            label="Event Name"
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>
        <v-col cols="4">
          <v-text-field
            readonly
            dense
            :value="Event.User"
            label="User Name"
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>
      </v-row>
      <v-row>
        <v-col>
          <v-text-field readonly dense label="Category" :value="Event.Category"></v-text-field>
        </v-col>
        <v-col>
          <v-text-field
            readonly
            dense
            :value="Event.Location"
            label="Location"
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>
        <v-col>
          <v-text-field
            readonly
            dense
            :value="Event.Organization"
            label="Organization"
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>
      </v-row>
      <v-row>
        <v-col>
          <v-text-field
            readonly
            dense
            :value="Event.StartTime"
            label="Start Time"
            type="time"
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>
        <v-col>
          <v-text-field
            readonly
            dense
            :value="Event.EndTime"
            label="End Time"
            type="time"
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>
        <v-col>
          <v-text-field
            readonly
            dense
            :value="Event.Attending + '/' + Event.Capacity"
            label="Event Capacity"
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>
      </v-row>
      <v-date-picker
        readonly
        color="rgb(231,75,74)"
        full-width
        v-model="Event.Date"
        no-title
      ></v-date-picker>
      <v-textarea
        readonly
        style="margin-top: 5%"
        outlined
        label="Comment"
        :value="Event.Comment"
      ></v-textarea>
    </v-container>
  </v-form>
</v-card>
